  "desc": "A beast with monstrous blood that is capable of eroding the boundaries of the world. \"Gold\" classified them as \"Alfisol.\"<br/>The previous eras, when giant monstrous beasts descended, large swarms of these hounds would go before them to deliquesce the borders of the world and open the way.",
